=== Pombert ''et al''. 2005 ===
A possible classification when Chlorophyta refers to one of the two clades of the Viridiplantae is shown below.<ref>Jean-Francxois Pombert et al 2005, [http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/content/22/9/1903.full.pdf The Chloroplast Genome Sequence of the Green Alga ''Pseudendoclonium akinetum'' (Ulvophyceae) Reveals Unusual Structural Features and New Insights into the Branching Order of Chlorophyte Lineages] Mol. Biol. Evol. 22(9) 1903–1918. {{DOI|10.1093/molbev/msi182}}</ref>
